{"tid":13252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"快訊／巧婦難為無米之炊 張國政不接手復興航空","createTime":"2016-11-30T03:33:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T03:33:06.000Z","uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e5eca8ba139c292a23f4c2c38baae2e9c902c97","tid":13252,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:33:06.000Z","msg":"前民航局長張國政今日上午召開記者會宣布，決定退出承接復興航空，支持政府對復興航空航權收回的決定，也強調張國政本人與團隊成員及親屬均無擁有復興航空公司或有關公司股票，並請政府支持爭取興航離職員工權益。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A-%E5%B7%A7%E5%A9%A6%E9%9B%A3%E7%82%BA%E7%84%A1%E7%B1%B3%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%8A-%E5%BC%B5%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%A5%E6%89%8B%E5%BE%A9%E8%88%88%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA-031547736.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E5%25B7%25A7%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E9%259B%25A3%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%2582%258A-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258E%25A5%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E8%2588%2588%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA-031547736.html&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=5c70e374\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A-%E5%B7%A7%E5%A9%A6%E9%9B%A3%E7%82%BA%E7%84%A1%E7%B1%B3%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%8A-%E5%BC%B5%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%A5%E6%89%8B%E5%BE%A9%E8%88%88%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA-031547736.html</a>"}]}